Titolo: Galak-Z: The Dimensional

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: Galak-Z: The Dimensional is a shooter video game by 17-Bit for Microsoft Windows, OS X, Linux and PlayStation 4. It was announced during Sony's pre-E3 2013 press conference in June 2013. 17-Bit CEO Jake Kazdal describes it as "modern Halo and Far Cry 3 combat in a 2-dimensional shell." Reflecting its inspiration in part by Japanese anime, the game is also known officially by the Japanese title of Uchuu Senshi Galak-Z (宇宙戦士ガラクZ, lit., "Space Soldier Galak-Z")